TITLE: Using Match Patterns in Meteor
DESCRIPTION: Provides examples of various 'Match' patterns available in Meteor's 'check' library for variable validation. These patterns allow you to match different types including any value, primitive types, integer, objects, and more with optional and conditional patterns.
