TITLE: Implementing Login Form in React for Meteor
DESCRIPTION: Creates a login form component using React hooks to handle user authentication in a Meteor application.
SOURCE: https://github.com/meteor/meteor/blob/devel/v3-docs/docs/tutorials/react/7.adding-user-accounts.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: jsx
