TITLE: Implementing Meteor Methods with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript code defining Meteor methods for CRUD operations on the 'another-customer' model.
SOURCE: https://github.com/meteor/meteor/blob/devel/docs/source/commandline.md#2025-04-22_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
