TITLE: Setting Up Global Configuration for jam:offline in Meteor
DESCRIPTION: This snippet provides the default global configuration object for 'jam:offline'. It specifies filters, sorting, limits, and other key settings for offline data management. Users can change these defaults using the 'Offline.configure' method. It is recommended to import the Offline module on both client and server sides.
SOURCE: https://github.com/meteor/meteor/blob/devel/v3-docs/docs/community-packages/offline.md#2025-04-22_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
