TITLE: Circular Reference Causing Infinite Loop in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This example illustrates a circular reference in reactive computations that leads to an infinite loop. It demonstrates the importance of avoiding circular dependencies in reactive code to prevent the Tracker flush cycle from getting stuck.
