TITLE: Incorrect Usage: Missing buildSubmodule in Submodule | meteor-rpc | TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates incorrect creation of submodules by either calling build instead of buildSubmodule, or omitting both. This leads to submodules that won't be properly attached or namespaced and should be avoided. Highlights the requirement to use buildSubmodule for any submodule intended for hierarchical composition.
