TITLE: Async Callback Without Fiber
DESCRIPTION: Example showing problematic async callback usage in Meteor that fails due to missing fiber context.
SOURCE: https://github.com/meteor/meteor/blob/devel/guide/source/using-npm-packages.md#2025-04-22_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// Inside a Meteor method definition
updateGitHubFollowers() {
  github.user.getFollowingFromUser({
    user: 'stubailo'
  }, (err, res) => {
    // Using a collection here will throw an error
    // because the asynchronous code is not in a fiber
    Followers.insert(res);
  });
}
```

