TITLE: Error Message When Updating to Meteor 2.13
DESCRIPTION: Common error message encountered when updating to Meteor 2.13 related to incorrect data check in the zlib module. This issue was solved in Meteor 2.13.3.
SOURCE: https://github.com/meteor/meteor/blob/devel/guide/source/2.13-migration.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
Error: incorrect data check
    at Zlib.zlibOnError [as onerror] (zlib.js:187:17)
 => awaited here:
 ...
    at /tools/cli/main.js:1165:7 {
  errno: -3,
  code: 'Z_DATA_ERROR'
  }
```

